        "description": {
          "value": "<p><em data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>Any creature not peacefully accompanied by Conna the Wise enters the room<br /><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>After [[/gmroll 1d4 ]] rounds, </em>the paintings on the wall animate, showing a gruesome sight. The targets have to make a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"34\" data-pf2-traits=\"\" data-pf2-label=\"Gruesome Sight, DC 34\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save<em data-visibility=\"gm\">, after which the Flayed Giant rolls initiative.</em></p>\n<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Critical Success</strong>&nbsp;The target is unaffected.<br /><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed} for 1 round.<br /><strong>Failure&nbsp;</strong>The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed}for 2 rounds.<br /><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed} for 4 rounds and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 1} for 8 hours.</p>"
